# Project: leo-workstation

Flutter ops client — interpreter, customer, dispatcher workstations in one app.

## Read before editing

- `docs/release-plan.md` / `docs/client-map.md` — what to build
- `docs/architecture-overview.md` — MVVM + Riverpod (§1 feature scaffold checklist)
- `docs/platform-references.md` — links to `../leo-api` (never copy platform docs)
- `.pineapple/features/` — feature specs
- `.pineapple/phases/INDEX.md` — active phase

## Consult invariants & state (when needed)

| If you need… | Read |
|---|---|
| Load-bearing rules — what must not break | [`.pineapple/invariants-client.md`](.pineapple/invariants-client.md) — `INV-CLIENT-*` |
| As-built reality + recent decisions | [`.pineapple/state.md`](.pineapple/state.md) — Floor, Decisions |
