## Presentation & state (do not regress)

Full rules: [`.cursor/rules/state-management.mdc`](state-management.mdc) (`INV-CLIENT-STATE-1`…`3`).

- **Freezed notifier state** in `presentation/state/<feature>_state.dart`; **freezed UI state** in `presentation/state/<feature>_ui_state.dart`.
- **Async/business state lives in the feature `Notifier`** — never private `_loading`, `_submitting`, etc. on screens/widgets.
- **Views watch a derived UI provider co-located on the notifier file** (`authUiProvider`, `signupUiProvider`, `onboardingUiProvider`) — not a separate `presentation/providers/` file.
- **Repository calls only from notifiers** — widgets dispatch `ref.read(<notifier>.notifier).method()`; no `ref.read(<repo>Provider)` in `presentation/`.
- **Session navigation is redirect-driven** — no imperative `context.go` to role home after login / `completeOnboarding()`; router reacts to `AuthState`.
- **Extend existing `freezed` state arms with optional metadata** — do not add router-contract union arms without specs + `redirect.dart` (`INV-CLIENT-STATE-2`).

Reference slices: `lib/features/auth/`, `lib/features/onboarding/`.

## Data layer (DTO + entity)

- **Request bodies** → `data/dto/<feature>_dto.dart` (`freezed` + `json_serializable`, `toJson()`).
- **Domain types** → `domain/<feature>_entities.dart` (not `*_models.dart`); entity `fromJson` when wire matches domain.
- **Repositories** → `dto.toJson()` / `Entity.fromJson(requireJsonMap|List(...))` — never `response.data!`, `_map*`, or inline wire maps (`INV-CLIENT-SERIAL-1`).
- **API errors** → show server `message` via `mapUserFacingError`; branch on `ApiErrorCode` only for special UX (redirect, field highlight, session teardown). No client code→copy map (`INV-CLIENT-NET-2`). Reference: `lib/core/network/api_error.dart`.
- **No cross-feature `data/` imports** (`INV-CLIENT-ARCH-2`).

## Verification

- `flutter analyze` on edited files; `build_runner` after `freezed` / `json_serializable` changes.
- **Do not add or expand Flutter tests** unless the user explicitly asks (`INV-CLIENT-TEST-1`).

## Do NOT

- Build admin CRUD/reports in Flutter (BD7) · cross-import feature `data/` · persist PHI on device
- Private async flags or repo calls from `presentation/screens` or `widgets`
- `response.data!`, `_map*`, or inline wire maps in repositories
- Client code→copy maps or branching on API `message` text — show `message`; branch on `code` only
- Name domain files `*_models.dart`
